These are the following anti-goon rules that must be followed in order to mark a day.

For our purposes 'gooning' means watching porn without the immediate intent of masturbation 

1) Time must not exceed 30 minutes
The amount of time spent watching pornographic material must not exceed 30 minutes. Anything more is considered gooning. Of course, non pornographic masturbation is not included.

2) Ensure the morality of the pornographic material
If the point of the porn is that you shouldn't be seeing it, it is considered immoral. Immoral porn warrants an immediate reset of the counter

